<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.8">
<l>maṉaṅkoṇ ṭēṟumaṇ ṭōtari mutalā vaṅka yaṟkaṇṇi ṉārkaḷi ruppa</l>
<l>taṉaṅkoḷ meṉmulai nōkkamo ḻintu tañca mēcila tāpata reṉṟu</l>
<l>puṉaṅkoḷ meṉmayi laicciṟai vaitta puṉmai yāḷaṉeñ cilpuka veyta</l>
<l>vaṉaṅka ṉaṉṉatiṇ ṭōḷemmi rāmaṟ kañci ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We are frightened of our strong-armed Rāma, who is like incorporeal [Kāma]</l>
<l rend="indent">and who shot [arrows] to enter into the heart</l>
<l>Of the vile villain who, thinking [her] protection was but a few ascetics,</l>
<l rend="indent">kept captive the gentle peacock[-like lady]</l>
<l rend="indent">who had endured the wilderness,</l>
<l>Ceasing his gaze at the gold-bearing, soft breasts so that ladies</l>
<l rend="indent">with lovely fish[-shaped] eyes,</l>
<l>The first of whom was Maṇḍodarī who had passionately captured his heart,</l>
<l rend="indent">remained [neglected]. Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
